Package com.cognifide.qa.bb.aem.ui

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FieldContainer
    AemElement that serves as a container for other AemElements.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AemContentFinder
    Represents content finder in a AEM page in authoring mode.
    AemContentFinderTab
    Single tab in a content finder.
    AemContentTree
    Exposes functionality of a content tree
    AemDialog
    This class represents dialog window.
    AemDialogFieldResolver
    Factory class that searches for the dialog field in the page and constructs a AemElement out of it.
    DialogFieldProvider
    This is a provider that produces values for PageObject fields that represent dialog fields.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description

    This enum lists all available ways to display results in ContentFinder.
